spirit:component.spirit:name: mm_to_lite

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M_AXI_LITE_TARGET_SLAVE_BASE_ADDR
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:displayName: C M AXI LITE TARGET SLAVE BASE ADDR
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: The master requires a target slave base address. // The master will initiate read and write transactions on the slave with base address specified here as a parameter.

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M_AXI_LITE_ADDR_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:displayName: C M AXI LITE ADDR WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of M_AXI address bus. // The master generates the read and write addresses of width specified as C_M_AXI_ADDR_WIDTH.

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_M_AXI_LITE_DATA_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:displayName: C M AXI LITE DATA WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of M_AXI data bus. // The master issues write data and accept read data where the width of the data bus is C_M_AXI_DATA_WIDTH

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_ID_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of ID for for write address, write data, read address and read data

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_AWUSER_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of optional user defined signal in write address channel

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_ARUSER_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of optional user defined signal in read address channel

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_WUSER_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of optional user defined signal in write data channel

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_RUSER_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of optional user defined signal in read data channel

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_BUSER_WIDTH
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:description: Width of optional user defined signal in write response channel
